Insider Activity


Individual




Scott Garrett Sleyster



Mr. Scott G. Sleyster, CFA MBA, is Chief Investment Officer & Senior Vice President at The Prudential Insurance Co. of America, Chief Investment Officer & Senior Vice President at Prudential Financial, Inc., a Member at The New York Society of Security Analysts, Inc., and Chief Investment Officer & Senior Vice President at The Prudential Variable Contract Real Property Account.
Mr. Sleyster was previously employed as Chief Investment Officer & Senior Vice President by The Prudential Insurance Co. of America. He also served on the board at Pruco Life Insurance Co., Pruco Life Insurance Company of New Jersey, Pruco Life of New Jersey Variable Contract Real Property A, and Pruco Life Variable Contract Real Property Account.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Missouri and an MBA from Northwestern University.



