Executive Profile
Scott G. Sleyster  Chief Investment Officer and Senior Vice President, Prudential Financial, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 6 different industries.See Board Relationships57--
Background

		Mr. Scott G. Sleyster has been the Chief Investment Officer and Senior Vice President at Prudential Financial, Inc. since February 2013 and May, 2012 respectively. Mr. Sleyster has been Senior Vice President of The Prudential Insurance Company of America since 1999. He joined Prudential in 1987 and has made a number of significant contributions. He served as the President of the Guaranteed Products business and as Chief Financial Officer for the Employee Benefits Division. ... He began his career at Prudential in the Private Placement area of Prudential Capital. He served as Director at Pruco Life Insurance Company and Pruco Life Insurance Co. He served as Director of Pruco Life Variable Contract Real Property Account; Pruco Life of New Jersey Variable Contract Real Property Account; and Pruco Life Insurance Company of New Jersey. He serves as a Trustee of North Star Academy Charter School of Newark. Mr. Sleyster has an MBA from Northwestern University and earned a finance degree.Read Full Background




